H2]/[C18O] were derived. However, the obtained ranges in the\nabundance ratios show that if an accurate analysis of the molecular gas is\nrequired, the use of the canonical values may introduce some bias. Thus, it is\nimportant to consider how the gas is irradiated by the far ultraviolet photons\nacross the molecular cloud. The analysis of X is a good tool to perform that.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Nov 2019 13:45:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
